==[[Irish]]==
#[[w:Teachta Dála|Teachta Dála]],  a member of Dáil Éireann, the lower chamber of the Parliament of the Republic of Ireland. 
====Usage Note====
* In English the abbreviation TD is normally used, with TDs as the plural (the full form of which in Irish is Teachtaí Dála).
* The letters follow the name of the member when used as a title, eg, ''Mr Bertie Ahern TD''.